example.para:
The number of rows in a  table of k picks
from n choices is:



Combinatoric.BinomialCoefficient (n, k)

The number of rows in a  table of k picks
from n choices is:



Combinatoric.BinomialCoefficient (k+n-1, k)

member.exception:
When length of source is greater than 20 or contains invalid data;
When source contains out of range values;
When choices is less than 0 or greater than 20.
